24
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:43,960
Echo Log — Charlotte Re:Lord
残響ログ Charlotte Re:Lord

25
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:47,030
Bring back the vanished night
消えた夜を 呼び戻せ

26
00:01:47,030 --> 00:01:50,850
I won't let it end unrecorded
未記録のまま 終わらせない

27
00:01:50,850 --> 00:01:54,040
Carve a path with this voice
